    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3145350/extras/d5b96aa7444e8d06249cd74c4b986369.poster.avif?t=1765347847\" width=616 height=90 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3145350/extras/d5b96aa7444e8d06249cd74c4b986369.webm?t=1765347847\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3145350/extras/d5b96aa7444e8d06249cd74c4b986369.mp4?t=1765347847\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这是 Cats and Seek 系列的第五款游戏。为了庆祝 Toge Productions 的周年庆，我们将探索 Toge Land，并向那里居住的猫咪们问好 😃<br><br>😻 一起和 Toge Land 的猫咪们玩捉迷藏吧！ <br>❤️     你能找到它们所有吗？ ❤️<br><br>🎮 1 个关卡 - 😻 105 只猫 - 🔆 亮度设置 <br>🔔 免费提示 - 💾 保存系统 - 🔍 放大 <br>🔉 可爱的猫咪声音 - 🎮 支持手柄 <br><br><strong>🎨 选择你喜欢的颜色</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3145350/extras/d331e25d948eb607d6f2b8d287736687.poster.avif?t=1765347847\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3145350/extras/d331e25d948eb607d6f2b8d287736687.webm?t=1765347847\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3145350/extras/d331e25d948eb607d6f2b8d287736687.mp4?t=1765347847\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>📷 照片模式</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3145350/extras/38d4d88cbc3fdbc0de19f2950ed13707.poster.avif?t=1765347847\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3145350/extras/38d4d88cbc3fdbc0de19f29